  "original_title": "6 \u0b86\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0bae\u0bc6\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 200 \u0bb0\u0bc2\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "For the 6th time, the price of a bucket of cement has increased by Rs 200",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Cement Distributors Association has said that the price of a 50 kg bucket of cement has been increased by 200 rupees.",
        "While a 50 kg bucket of cement was seen at Rs 900 a year ago, the price of a bucket of cement has been increased 6 times within this one year period.",
        "The Cement Distributors' Association points out that due to fuel shortage in the country and increase in fuel prices, they are facing massive inconvenience and traffic problems in transporting cement buckets to various places.",
        "It is noteworthy that due to the increase in cement prices, those involved in the construction of houses and buildings are facing a massive setback in their industry."
      ],
